.
.
When we slow down and make time for recovery our bodies can heal and rebalance. Sometimes in these transition periods we can see symptoms on our skin. Acne on the chin and jaw as hormones shift, eczema or other irritations if the gut is off, etc. It's all very personal to your individual situation. Remember to give yourself grace in this period and see these symptoms as what they are, signs telling you something is in need of rebalancing. 
